  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd : '\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd, \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bcb\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd\u201c \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb7\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Lawyers take to the streets against the government: 'Ranil, let's defeat the Kota maneuver' slogan",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "With the slogan 'Let's get rid of the government that is persecuting the people', the lawyers took to the streets today (1) Friday and carried out a massive satyagraha protest.",
        "They started the satyagraha protest at 9.00 am in front of Pudukadai court complex, Colombo 12.",
        "Ranil, let's defeat the Kota maneuver, stop hunting down lawyers, do not hunt down human rights activists, do not lie - they spearheaded the satyagraha struggle carrying various banners including Kota house cell.",
        "In this situation, the lawyers who carried out the satyagraha from the side of the road in front of the Colombo Chief Justice's Court then marched towards the fort from there through the backwaters. Hundreds of lawyers attended.",
        "At this juncture, the lawyers who marched in this situation prevented the fort -wing -World Trade Center building near the Bank Mawatha area.",
        "As the lawyers marched towards the Presidential Palace, a large contingent of police was mobilized to restrict their movement.",
        "Lawyers chanted slogans against the president, the police and the government. The protest, which lasted for more than two hours, ended at 1.00 pm.",
        "The lawyers mentioned that the police are on the side of the people and the lawyers are on the side of the people and raised various slogans against the President."
      ],
